commitResults.messageBody:
Add a new command, AssignTeamCommand, to create a team for assignment to pre-existing projects. This command facilitates the creation of teams within the application. Additionally, create AssignTeamCommandParser to handle parsing logic for this command.

To support the functionality of AssignTeamCommand, modify AddressBookParser to incorporate necessary changes.

This commit addresses the need for creating and parsing team-related commands, enhancing the project's functionality.

Resolves: issue#64
